text: Thánh Thiên (10-43 AD) was a princess of Vietnam. She participated in the Trung sisters' rebellion against the Han Chinese. As the legend goes, Thiên was born in the village of Bich UyenThanh, 35. Thánh committed suicide because she did not want to be captured.Quýnh, 88. == References == Category:10 births Category:43 deaths
